{"article_id":"P0LRmeZbLKum5Dbh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"\" I did not email any classified material to anyone... \"","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"proclaimed Hillary Clinton at her March press conference in an attempt","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to quell questions about the unsecure server","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"she used for all State Department business .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Cleverly , Clinton dodged the fact","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"that she received classified email on that vulnerable server ,","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"conduct also in violation of 18 USC 1924 ,","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"which makes it a crime to have classified information at an \" unauthorized location. \"","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Just ask General David Petraeus .","depth":3},{"id":9,"text":"This week ' s disclosure","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that Clinton ' s unsecured emails contained Top Secret material","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"- one of the highest classifications -","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"calls into question just about every phrase","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"the former Secretary of State and her campaign staff have uttered","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to excuse her conduct .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Let ' s cut the spin","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"and identify her email transgressions for what they are :","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"gross mismanagement of classified material","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that happens to violate the law .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"One Clinton spokesperson proffered","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"because the material was not specifically marked ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Clinton could not have been aware","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that the material was classified .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"In that same March news conference Clinton bragged","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that she was \" certainly aware of the classified requirements. \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Apparently not .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Government officials are required to keep their correspondence on the appropriate government server","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"so the material can be classified","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"before it is mistakenly sent to an \" unauthorized location. \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Clinton ' s argument ignores her actual misconduct .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"The reason","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"the documents were not marked","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"is because she never submitted them for clearance .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Let ' s cut the spin","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and identify Hillary Clinton 's email transgressions for what they are :","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"gross mismanagement of classified material","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that happens to violate the law .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"As former intelligence professionals , we are well aware","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that strict guidelines are required","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"for handling classified information .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Briefings","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that include classified information","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"are held in Sensitive Compartmented Information Facilities , rooms with elaborate protections","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to minimize eavesdropping .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Telephone conversations of classified information are conducted via secure phones .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Emails","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"that might contain classified information","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"are sent only through secure networks ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"not through","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"- heaven forbid -","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"a personal server in a basement .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Clinton should have been sufficiently aware of what was \" classifiable. \"","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Classified subjects are frequently discussed sans paper .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Oral briefings are common for government officials .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Many times the only method","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"of briefing a Member of Congress on a specific matter","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"is face to face with CIA personnel","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"so questions can be asked","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"and answered .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Nevertheless ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"when a government official receives an oral classified briefing ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"he or she is obligated to understand the nature of the information and to protect it appropriately .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Ignoring her responsibility","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to be aware","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"when she is given classified information ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Clinton suggested","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that the matter was overblown","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"because the documents were not classified at the time","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"she had custody","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and \" various parts of the government \" are \" disagree [ ing ] \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"about whether the material should be classified .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Not so .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"According to the intelligence community ' s Inspector General ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"whose office conducted a random search of Clinton ' s emails","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"and found 10 percent classified","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"( at a level lower than Top Secret ) ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"those emails were \" classified","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"when they were sent","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"and are classified now . \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Clinton may have more legal challenges .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Her repeated assertions","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that she turned all government documents over to the State Department","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"can be contradicted in two ways","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that culminate into criminal conduct .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"It has already been shown that in Sydney Blumenthal 's production of emails to the Benghazi Committee , they included at least 15 Clinton emails","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"related to Benghazi","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that are nowhere to be found in Clinton ' s production to the State Department .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Is this obstruction of justice ?","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Clinton ' s sworn statement under penalty of perjury to a federal judge","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that she turned over \" all \" emails \"","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that were or potentially federal records \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"can also be challenged","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"if her server ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"which she has finally agreed to turn over to investigators ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"reveals the content of the deleted emails .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"To escape a perjury or obstruction of justice charge ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Clinton had to have produced all government documents","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"or have been very good at deleting .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"The more important question is how does she escape being charged with 18 USC 1924 , a law","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"that she has already violated ?","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":109,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":106,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":0,"right":103,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":1,"right":102,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit